%F A383039 a(n) = 2*Lucas(n)^2 - 1.
%F A383039 a(n) = 2*A001254(n) - 1.
%e A383039 For n=3, the short leg is A382379(3,1) = 5 and the long leg is A382379(3,2) = 12 so the sum of the legs is then a(2) = 5 + 12 = 17.
